Name: Achievement Clicker 2019
About the game: Achievement Clicker 2019 is the new 2019 version of Achievement Clicker, its a game in the genre timekiller-clicker, where your main objective is to get the most Achievements! Start out by clicking and get the Achievements! The game has a store where you can buy Achievements! Features: - 5000 Achievements! - More items / upgrades! - Amazing design! - Amazing music!
